---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Mid-Century Modern Wedding Invitations | Hummingbird Social Studio';
const description = 'Modern retro wedding invitation suites inspired by mid-century modern design, Palm Springs weddings, vintage typography, and minimalist aesthetics.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Mid-Century Modern Wedding Invitations</h1>

    <p>
      Clean typography, retro color palettes, vintage-inspired layouts, and timeless modern design.
      Our mid-century modern wedding invitation suites are inspired by Palm Springs weddings,
      modern architecture, desert aesthetics, and iconic mid-century design elements.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether you are planning a colorful retro wedding, a minimalist modern celebration,
      or a stylish Palm Springs-inspired event, these invitation suites are designed to
      feel elegant, artistic, and memorable.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Inspired by Retro Modern Design</h2>

    <p>
      Mid-century modern weddings continue to grow in popularity because they combine
      vintage charm with clean modern aesthetics. These invitation suites often feature
      geometric layouts, bold typography, earthy color palettes, abstract shapes,
      minimalist compositions, and artistic retro details.
    </p>

    <p>
      Popular wedding venues and destinations for this style include Palm Springs,
      California desert resorts, modern architecture venues, boutique hotels,
      art galleries, and outdoor modern weddings.
    </p>

    <h2>Popular Mid-Century Modern Wedding Invitation Styles</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Palm Springs wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Retro modern wedding suites</li>
      <li>Minimalist geometric invitations</li>
      <li>Vintage-inspired typography designs</li>
      <li>Colorful abstract wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Boho modern wedding stationery</li>
      <li>1960s inspired wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Desert modern wedding invitations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Designed for Stylish Modern Weddings</h2>

    <p>
      Our invitation suites are created for couples who appreciate intentional design,
      modern aesthetics, and elevated details. Each suite can include save the dates,
      wedding invitations, RSVP cards, details cards, welcome signage, menus,
      seating charts, and day-of wedding stationery.
    </p>

    <p>
      We focus on cohesive wedding branding that creates a consistent visual experience
      from your invitations to your wedding day details.
    </p>

    <h2>Custom Mid-Century Modern Wedding Stationery</h2>

    <p>
      Looking for a fully custom design? We can create personalized invitation suites
      tailored to your venue, wedding colors, typography preferences, and overall
      wedding aesthetic.
    </p>

    <p>
      From modern minimalist layouts to colorful retro-inspired designs, we help create
      wedding stationery that feels unique to your celebration.
    </p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>What is a mid-century modern wedding style?</h3>
    <p>
      Mid-century modern weddings are inspired by the design movement of the 1940s–1960s,
      featuring clean lines, bold typography, geometric shapes, vintage aesthetics,
      and modern minimalist influences.
    </p>

    <h3>Are these invitation suites customizable?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Colors, typography, layouts, wording, and wedding details can all be customized.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer matching wedding day stationery?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Matching signage, menus, escort cards, welcome signs, and other wedding day
      paper goods can be designed to match your invitation suite.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer digital and printed invitations?</h3>
    <p>
      We offer both digital invitation designs and professionally printed wedding stationery.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
